440
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,040
Tapi tidak disangka…

441
00:31:10,080 --> 00:31:12,200
Apakah insiden manusia
memukuli siluman kecil sampai mati

442
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:14,160
